com.phunware.mapping.library.maps

Class PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.phunware.mapping.library.maps.PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder

  • public class PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder provides the ability to manage map overlays, and create PwBuildingMapManager objects
    See Also:
    GoogleMap, PwOnMapDataLoadedCallback, PwOnFloorChangedCallback, PwRouteCallback, PwOnCameraChangeListener, BitmapDescriptor
